      <title>美元的超级大国地位面临国内外动荡的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/janet-yellen-s-successor-will-have-to-steer-the-dollar-through-rough-waters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据纸士兵的独家摘录，华盛顿激进地使用制裁和加剧的党派之争正在动摇外国人对美元的信心。]]></description>
