    <item>
      <title>共和党议员表示，字节跳动投资者可能会在 TikTok 销售中获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/bytedance-investors-could-win-in-tiktok-sale-gop-lawmaker-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位共和党议员表示，如果 TikTok 出售该应用程序，TikTok 中国母公司的投资者将受益，因为撤资将消除不确定性来源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/bytedance-investors-could-win-in-tiktok-sale-gop-lawmaker-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 18:12:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京在俄罗斯选举中取得创纪录的胜利，推动乌克兰战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/putin-takes-record-election-win-to-press-russia-s-war-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[弗拉基米尔·普京(Vladimir Putin)获得了再任俄罗斯总统六年的机会，以加强在乌克兰的战争并挑战西方，克里姆林宫声称在一次投票中他获得了创纪录的公众支持，而投票的结果是预先确定的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/putin-takes-record-election-win-to-press-russia-s-war-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 18:08:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国、法国带头呼吁欧洲投资银行加强国防融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/germany-france-lead-call-for-eib-to-step-up-defense-financing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国和法国与其他 12 个欧盟国家一起呼吁欧洲投资银行增加国防融资，以此作为应对俄罗斯侵略的增强欧盟安全的手段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/germany-france-lead-call-for-eib-to-step-up-defense-financing</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 17:22:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰农民封锁德国边境附近的主要高速公路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/polish-farmers-block-key-highway-near-german-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰农民开始封锁德国边境附近的一条主要高速公路，以抗议从乌克兰进口粮食和欧盟有关农业的气候倡议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/polish-farmers-block-key-highway-near-german-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 15:42:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟通过74亿欧元援助计划加强与埃及的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/eu-boosts-ties-with-egypt-through-eur7-4-billion-support-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟承诺向埃及提供 74 亿欧元（81 亿美元）的一揽子援助计划，这是国际社会为提振这个被视为对地区稳定至关重要的北非国家陷入困境的经济而采取的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/eu-boosts-ties-with-egypt-through-eur7-4-billion-support-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 14:05:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>持续热浪导致南苏丹学校无限期关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/sustained-heat-wave-shutters-schools-indefinitely-in-south-sudan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于热浪可能导致气温高达 45 摄氏度（113 华氏度），南苏丹政府下令全国所有学校无限期关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/sustained-heat-wave-shutters-schools-indefinitely-in-south-sudan</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 13:39:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡反驳舒默的“不恰当”批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/netanyahu-vows-to-continue-war-despite-mounting-global-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡周日对美国参议院多数党领袖查克·舒默的言论进行了反击，舒默上周呼吁以色列举行选举以罢免现任政府。]]></description>
